    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're trying to be kind, but you're not in my shoes. it feels like a cycle that'll never end, just more pain and more inconvenience for everyone i love. they deserve to have their lives back, to not have to worry about me every single day. it almost feels like a mercy, doesn't it? to just step out of the way so they can finally breathe?",
