      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain you feel is real, and it is understandable that you wish to protect them from your burdens, but your presence is not a problem they can simply step away from. Your children have always loved you, even when you were difficult, and they will not forgive you if you disappear when you are most vulnerable. Please do not make a decision to end your life, as there is no mercy in letting go and only suffering in the silence that follows.",
